title: On Tuesdays
author: SortByNode
pages:
#- I’m drunk on Tuesday,
I didn’t make it half way through the week,
I’m drunk on Tuesday,
and some days I can barely speak,
and one day I’ll be fine,
but until that day is mine,
#- I’m drunk on Tuesdays,
I’m drunk on Wednesday too,
I’ll drink it all red, black, and blue
and one day I’ll be strong,
but until that day comes along,
I’m drunk on Tuesdays,
#- -The 4onthefloor
§1http://youtu.be/ZIv0xHTqDTE§r
